  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    British Embassy Bucharest: calls for bids on climate change
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Applications for projects related to the UK’s priorities as part of the climate change agenda and host of COP26 in 2021 to be </p>

  </div>
</div>

